* Block 09: Startup Circuit
* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A
*
* Mechanism: Very weak gate pulldown + strong MN_pu overshoot limiter
*
* Strategy: MN_pu (W=100u source follower) dominates over the weak
* gate pulldown (R_gate=2MΩ, MN_gate W=1u L=2u). Gate stays near
* BVDD-Vth during startup → pass device barely on → slow PVDD ramp.
* When PVDD reaches threshold, MN_gate turns off and error amp takes over.
*
.subckt startup bvdd pvdd gate gnd vref startup_done ea_en

* ================================================================
* PVDD threshold detector — trips at ~3.9V
* ================================================================
XR_top pvdd sense_mid gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=2 l=8200
XR_bot sense_mid gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=2 l=1800
XMN_det det_out sense_mid gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=10e-6 l=1e-6

* 30MΩ pull-up
XR_pu bvdd det_out gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=15001

* ================================================================
* Gate pulldown — VERY weak to keep gate near BVDD
* ================================================================
* R_gate = 2MΩ directly to GND through MN_gate (switched).
* After startup, MN_gate off → no current through R_gate.
* MN_gate: minimum-size W=0.42u L=20u → extremely weak pull.
XR_gate gate pull_mid gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=501
XMN_gate pull_mid det_out gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=0.42e-6 l=20e-6

* ================================================================
* BVDD gate pull-up (overshoot limiter)
* ================================================================
* W=100u source follower dominates during startup.
* Keeps gate ≈ BVDD - Vth → Vsg ≈ Vth → pass device barely on.
* 28 parallel W=100u instances = effective 2.8mm
XMN_pu1  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu2  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu3  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu4  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu5  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu6  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu7  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu8  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu9  bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu10 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu11 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu12 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu13 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu14 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu15 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu16 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
XMN_pu17 bvdd bvdd gate gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=100e-6 l=1e-6
